{"tid":2421410,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友一齊左一個月 佢就想扑嘢","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T13:22:56.000Z","uid":61543,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"da903bdfed1f829769b4d31e40aa06935caa48d3","tid":2421410,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:14:51.000Z","msg":"我18歲，男朋友21歲<br />\n兩個都喺處，初戀<br />\n依家一齊咗個幾月<br />\n<br />\n我地識咗2年<br />\n佢身邊一直都冇咩男仔frd<br />\n未一齊之前覺得佢喺正正經經<br />\n怕怕醜醜嗰啲男仔<br />\n一齊咗一星期左右<br />\n上咗佢屋企等佢換衫出街<br />\n我一入去就坐咗喺梳化睇片<br />\n佢換完就行嚟我側邊同我一齊睇<br />\n睇咗陣佢就話:不如一齊瞓喺度睇啦，坐喺度睇好攰<br />\n咁我就訓咗喺度<br />\n睇完片佢無啦啦壓係我身上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問我可唔可以同佢扑野...<br />\n我話:唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢就話:好啦咁算啦<br />\n我隨口問佢:你想扑野你有套咩？<br />\n佢竟然答我:冇呀...男男唔會有事<br />\n聽完我就一直好介意<br />\n<br />\n個晚佢睇得出我唔喺幾開心就攬住我同我say sorry，話唔會再講依啲住<br />\n<br />\n點知過左一星期佢又問多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到我依家成日諗佢喺真喺鐘意我定......"},{"pid":"31d908f38483765628f4569e17298936233ee5aa","tid":2421410,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"感建分<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2fe4e39ca390b760b164820145206980338265","tid":2421410,"uid":99725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"88783bf4f9c6dcdf51a3339841b421acb382c286","tid":2421410,"uid":376479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"想含你"},{"pid":"5a28036c11e1f90171fae599accd6beec00464a9","tid":2421410,"uid":240406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:17:59.000Z","msg":"This"},{"pid":"870df8117e1e6e5aa4fc95dd3ac79bc63db2ff68","tid":2421410,"uid":165136,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:18:06.000Z","msg":"其實你誤會咗你男朋友<br />\n<br />\n佢未一齊已經想